Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在被星光照射的頂屋裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,獨自一人聆聽著天空的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用玻璃的繃帶遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都是孤獨的馬戲團孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤身一人的悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,震動的繃帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,撼動著心靈……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用溫柔的眼神期待與某人的相會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我耳邊細語「請留在我身邊」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Silent Voice
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.30,0:01:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬士文在亞古捷斯的空域死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是哈曼對這件事毫不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第四十六話 共震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些傢伙是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明的新人類部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類部隊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我方勢力薄弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他派那種東西出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.67,0:01:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我怎麼可能逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:10.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,準備好了沒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了古利明大人\n我們就算犧牲生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要殲滅哈曼的艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們算什麼阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,請撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是哈曼大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別衝動\n要衡量情況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回去就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種敵人根本無法應付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去新亞加瑪\n在觀察戰況吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.79,0:04:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布拉度艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.92,0:04:03.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幸好你回來了\n莉娜.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是救我的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道,馬茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好久不見了,布拉度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,馬茜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在地球的表現很活躍阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.71,0:04:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一個女人能做到什麼程度\n那是可想而知的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來,這是你太太與你兒子的錄影帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你至少該寫封信阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在第三殖民地的戰況好像很緊張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的,許多年輕人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也在那個空域戰鬥阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像過去的你們一樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我打算去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我哥哥馬沙的下落嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒時間搜索他阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這場戰爭完全感覺不到\n馬沙的個人意識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連哈曼的也沒有感覺到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也許他在某個地方\n看著我們所做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且在沉思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想說他在等候時機嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這確實是我哥哥的作風阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不覺得危險嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只有想念的新人類是很可悲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:37.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在做準備\n等著感到厭煩而展開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想看哥哥變成那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他乾脆死了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.46,0:05:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,野心與紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.73,0:05:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我覺得哥哥好像\n會被宇宙的大意至左右著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是這樣嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰!是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.41,0:06:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擅自跑到我的腦中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全面通知新人類部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把孟沙切離開去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是,孟沙分離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孟沙分離完畢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,修正方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓孟沙去撞擊哈曼軍艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.28,0:06:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼\n想統治世界的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是造成你毀滅的原因阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的孟沙開始移動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們想用那巨物撞上哈曼艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來如此,先撞散敵人編隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在一口氣擊滅新人類部隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候戰力比例就不是問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.92,0:06:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類部隊交給我解決吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿,捷度,補給...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒那個時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在不打敗古利明的話...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奧干的艦隊在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要拖到什麼時候才來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些雜亂的東西是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行動多不方便阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是飛盤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丟出去使用\n可以混亂敵人耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.14,0:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孟沙開始炮擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦隊分散開去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫MS隊上前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孟沙是新吉翁的象徵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他竟然拿來當盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡的古利明,真該死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我來守後方\n你上前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,達卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼伊,藍斯,那傢伙給我對付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我說過不會讓你過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你偷走哈曼大人的\n亞古捷斯還可以說什麼話?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孟沙還你們了不是嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哼,你能逃到什麼時候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?有別的氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那光波沒什麼...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼伊!姬娜大人拜託你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要礙事,滾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,藍斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人,請退後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦?是那傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種程度的飛彈不算什麼阿\n波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別妨礙捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快離開這架MS吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.45,0:09:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才想闖入我體內的是你嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度不是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.43,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跟捷度在一起很舒服的\n為什麼你不瞭解阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別過來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要使我混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?打中了卻沒效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有奇怪的盾牌嗎?波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那只是小孩在駕駛阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.04,0:10:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別聽古利明的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的防衛線斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼的MS部隊衝進去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達隊伍呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像進入防衛線裏面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他們只有三架MS...就跑去亞古捷斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反擊太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要撞上了\n不,擦過而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孟沙航道改變了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我方戰力減少15%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯加快速度\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讓亞古捷斯和柯亞3接觸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼...這次不會向孟沙那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,給你輕易必過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,捷度進去裏面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他想死嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧\n真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確認方位\n這次換亞古捷斯過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不能喪失亞古捷失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派間諜\n潛入亞古捷思改變方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.86,0:12:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是...我知道了,捷度\n你進入亞古捷斯了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明就在裏面嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人MS進入M區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我方的MS部隊在幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世的情況很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她直接飛回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的精神催眠\n不是最完美了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照理說應該是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才她的波動太混亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,為什麼回來?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾...波蕾在妨礙我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.69,0:13:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你振作一點\n波蕾在很久以前就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是被高達騙了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打倒他,這樣...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的頭痛會好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.23,0:13:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你的力量必須送給古利明我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明大人,你要幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已你和我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把高達打進宇宙的黑暗之中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達?是露卡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.77,0:14:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了,打倒想束縛你的敵人吧,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,束縛我的,敵人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主螢幕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有人可以妨礙我們前進的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,你在幹什麼阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!你在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死那個高達,就會舒服些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消滅它?\n對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,波蕾二世!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.71,0:15:39.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為古利明做事對你沒有益處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你害我痛苦的要命\n還說什麼風涼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是你必須打倒的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.04,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想當古利明的木偶嗎?波蕾二世!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,回來,他是敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,古利明是拿你當道具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有非戰不可的正義阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而你沒有正義,你為何而戰呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你打仗,是因為你是士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你駕駛高達,是情勢所逼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我自己選擇苛刻的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會後悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你沒有由心理涌起的衝動嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種人渣\n從我面前消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.87,0:16:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道這裏的人已經因為慾望\n而扭曲理念犯錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我...所以我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.09,0:16:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你感受的忿怒和不平就是理由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.19,0:16:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘉美尤不是受人命令的\n他是自願戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他相信它能拯救世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哥哥,相信自己的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.87,0:17:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是背負大家的意識而戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家的意識?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的好像很有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我問你,你的原點來自何處?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,培育一切生命的地球吧,是我們的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沙比家的血統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只佔其中數千億分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果非要為了那血統而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在亞古捷斯就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,地球受到污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們殖民地又舊又腐敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:51.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在人類全體\n必須重頭再來才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像你這種為小事\n而耿耿於懷的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不打倒你,地球就沒有明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.30,0:18:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被血統束縛的人\n是人類的絆腳石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.64,0:18:08.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能容許人類的這個可能性\n為了你的自我滿足而被握脆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.87,0:18:09.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是哥哥嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,頭好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有他的存在\n你的頭痛是不會停止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,捷度說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度嗎...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,過來吧\n波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在說什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是我的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別被搞亂阿,過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.19,0:18:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,戰鬥吧\n住手阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要被敵人迷惑到何時?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我討厭大家\n全部給我消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.59,0:18:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這光芒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,快救波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.21,0:18:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世想來我們這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,這樣才對的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,殺死捷度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達是打不死的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明\n不許你再利用波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少囉唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,帶我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來\n放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說過你喜歡我\n我不會忘記的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你嗎?露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我竟然死在你手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古利明的波動消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入亞古捷斯的間諜\n傳回通訊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的推進裝置被破壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法改變方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,全軍撤退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS也後退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定要活著回來阿\n捷度.桑達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到時候再跟你了結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯和柯亞3會相撞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒辦法聯絡嗎?\n不行,無法通訊阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要去哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去接人阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣下去會被衝擊波波及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不能看著他們死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.54,0:21:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不知道後果多嚴重\n才會說這種話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代理艦長!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信捷度他們吧,會逃出來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,露卡和艾莉的命很大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,新亞加瑪,後退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爆炸使得亞古捷斯遠離了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度他們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯的爆炸擴大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.47,0:21:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,看情況是逃不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.31,0:22:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是ZZ高達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MK2和Z高達在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,聽見了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,聽見了,伊萊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.88,0:22:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉她們呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她們沒事,在我這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.71,0:22:17.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比查,對不起,讓你擔心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們馬上就回來了\n知道了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.92,0:22:23.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嚇我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.78,0:22:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,波蕾二世,加油阿\n你不可以死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成百 成萬 上億的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為何只是閃耀而已 展示你言語的能力吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在我也能不回頭地 讓心靈出發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若能把多如繁星的生命儲存的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把整個銀河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,化作緊握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我仍未能看見宇宙的路標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,手掌觸摸著一千萬年的光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了和我做個了斷 哈曼出擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.28,0:23:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高潔！帥氣！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.66,0:23:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,輸了就會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.02,0:23:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這可不是在開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…好強的力量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.23,0:24:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,「誰來…！」不小心就這樣想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.96,0:24:05.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ 戰士再臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難道我被哈曼喜歡上了？

